        </item>
        <item>
            <title>BBC 將封鎖 OpenAI 抓取內容作訓練　不過對未來 AI 生成報導抱開放態度</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2023/10/07/generative-ai-at-the-bbc/fun-tech/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=generative-ai-at-the-bbc</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2023/10/07/generative-ai-at-the-bbc/fun-tech/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[藍骨]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Sat, 07 Oct 2023 08:40:44 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[科技趣聞]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[BBC]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[生成式 AI]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1197943</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>大型的 AI 模型在訓練的時候通常都需要使用大量的數據，而在網上抓取各種內容就自然是個常見的做法，不過也因此引起媒體和出版社的不滿。BBC 方面最近就公佈未來應對生成式 AI 的方針。<br /><span id="more-1197943"></span></p><p>BBC 方面在最新公佈的網誌中表示，面對生成式 AI 的科技創新熱潮，他們也必須與時並進。其中對於 OpenAI 等科技企業的內容抓取，將會採取方法禁止，這個做法與其他大型媒體例如 CNN、紐約時報、路透社和其他新聞組織一致。BBC 表示，這個做法是要保護授權付費用戶的權益，而未經許可使用其內容進行訓練，也不符合公眾利益。</p><p>雖然在這方面變得嚴格，不過 BBC 對於 AI 科技整體而言態度相當正面，他們表示，相信生成式 AI 可以為 BBC 帶來重要的機會，哂他們可以為觀眾和社會提供更大的價值，同時改善工作效率。他們提出了三個應用生成式 AI 的原則，包括：</p><ol><li>以公眾利益為先</li><li>優先考慮人才和創意</li><li>保持開放和透明</li></ol><p>BBC 將會在未來幾個月開展新的計劃，探索在其製作和營運中應用生成式 AI 的可能性，研究當中帶來的優勢和風險，特別是道德、法律和版權問題，以及仍然存在爭議的假消息和偏見風險。</p><p>來源：<a href="https://www.bbc.co.uk/mediacentre/articles/2023/generative-ai-at-the-bbc/">BBC</a></p><h2> 最新影片</h2><div class="video-container"><iframe loading="lazy" title="最新影片" width="500" height="281" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/videoseries?list=PLiEPZioiGtHw9_9gm4Ty0_pTEviOKNvfl" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" allowfullscreen=""></iframe></div></p>
]]>
            </description>
            <wfw:commentRss>https://unwire.hk/2023/10/07/generative-ai-at-the-bbc/fun-tech/feed/</wfw:commentRss>
            <slash:comments>0</slash:comments>
        </item>
        <item>
            <title>Google Gboard 推真「Key CAPS」  敲擊腦袋打字</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2023/10/07/google-gboard-keycaps/life-tech/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=google-gboard-keycaps</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2023/10/07/google-gboard-keycaps/life-tech/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[Oscar]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Sat, 07 Oct 2023 06:34:47 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[生活科技]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[Gboard]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[Gboard CAPS]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1197875</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>日本 Google 每年都會推出與 Google 鍵盤（Gboard）有關的惡搞影片，今年日本 Google 則推出了「Gboard CAPS」「鍵帽」。</p><p><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1197889" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Gboard-CAPS-0-19-screenshot-694x390.png" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Gboard-CAPS-0-19-screenshot-694x390.png 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Gboard-CAPS-0-19-screenshot-1280x720.png 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Gboard-CAPS-0-19-screenshot-768x432.png 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Gboard-CAPS-0-19-screenshot-1536x864.png 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Gboard-CAPS-0-19-screenshot.png 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1197885" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Gboard-CAPS-0-32-screenshot-694x390.png" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Gboard-CAPS-0-32-screenshot-694x390.png 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Gboard-CAPS-0-32-screenshot-1280x720.png 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Gboard-CAPS-0-32-screenshot-768x432.png 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Gboard-CAPS-0-32-screenshot-1536x864.png 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Gboard-CAPS-0-32-screenshot.png 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1197888" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Gboard-CAPS-0-21-screenshot-694x390.png" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Gboard-CAPS-0-21-screenshot-694x390.png 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Gboard-CAPS-0-21-screenshot-1280x720.png 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Gboard-CAPS-0-21-screenshot-768x432.png 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Gboard-CAPS-0-21-screenshot-1536x864.png 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Gboard-CAPS-0-21-screenshot.png 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p>今年推出的 Gboard CAPS 實際上就是一頂和鍵盤上的鍵帽（Keycap）一模一樣的帽子。據日本 Google 表示，這頂 Gboard CAPS 內置陀螺儀，用家打字時只需面向不同方向，CAPS 就可以偵測用家想打甚麼字符，最後輕敲頭部就可以用藍牙傳輸結果至電腦、手機等。日本 Google 稱這種輸入法為「Atama Input」，意即「頭腦輸入」。</p><p><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1197887" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Gboard-CAPS-0-25-screenshot-694x390.png" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Gboard-CAPS-0-25-screenshot-694x390.png 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Gboard-CAPS-0-25-screenshot-1280x720.png 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Gboard-CAPS-0-25-screenshot-768x432.png 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Gboard-CAPS-0-25-screenshot-1536x864.png 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Gboard-CAPS-0-25-screenshot.png 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲CAPS 內置陀螺儀</p><p><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1197886" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Gboard-CAPS-0-26-screenshot-694x390.png" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Gboard-CAPS-0-26-screenshot-694x390.png 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Gboard-CAPS-0-26-screenshot-1280x720.png 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Gboard-CAPS-0-26-screenshot-768x432.png 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Gboard-CAPS-0-26-screenshot-1536x864.png 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Gboard-CAPS-0-26-screenshot.png 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲能夠偵測用家方向，從而知悉用家想打甚麼字</p><p><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1197884" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Gboard-CAPS-0-34-screenshot-694x390.png" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Gboard-CAPS-0-34-screenshot-694x390.png 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Gboard-CAPS-0-34-screenshot-1280x720.png 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Gboard-CAPS-0-34-screenshot-768x432.png 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Gboard-CAPS-0-34-screenshot-1536x864.png 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Gboard-CAPS-0-34-screenshot.png 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲再以藍牙傳輸至你的裝置</p><p><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1197883" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Gboard-CAPS-0-11-screenshot-694x390.png" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Gboard-CAPS-0-11-screenshot-694x390.png 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Gboard-CAPS-0-11-screenshot-1280x720.png 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Gboard-CAPS-0-11-screenshot-768x432.png 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Gboard-CAPS-0-11-screenshot-1536x864.png 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Gboard-CAPS-0-11-screenshot.png 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p>日本 Google 更表示 CAPS 可以選擇不同機械軸，例如青軸、茶軸、紅軸鍵盤版本。其更表示這種聲波可以刺激腦部發展，對智商有莫大脾益。除此之外，CAPS 更可為用家遮風擋雨。</p><p><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1197891" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Gboard-CAPS-0-47-screenshot-694x390.png" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Gboard-CAPS-0-47-screenshot-694x390.png 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Gboard-CAPS-0-47-screenshot-1280x720.png 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Gboard-CAPS-0-47-screenshot-768x432.png 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Gboard-CAPS-0-47-screenshot-1536x864.png 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Gboard-CAPS-0-47-screenshot.png 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p>有用家表示一直尋找頭戴式鍵盤，但苦無結果。他表示使用 CAPS 後感覺非常方便，他又指用家可以輕鬆裝備這頂帽子。</p><p><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1197892" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Gboard-CAPS-1-8-screenshot-694x390.png" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Gboard-CAPS-1-8-screenshot-694x390.png 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Gboard-CAPS-1-8-screenshot-1280x720.png 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Gboard-CAPS-1-8-screenshot-768x432.png 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Gboard-CAPS-1-8-screenshot-1536x864.png 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Gboard-CAPS-1-8-screenshot.png 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1197893" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Gboard-CAPS-1-11-screenshot-694x390.png" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Gboard-CAPS-1-11-screenshot-694x390.png 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Gboard-CAPS-1-11-screenshot-1280x720.png 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Gboard-CAPS-1-11-screenshot-768x432.png 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Gboard-CAPS-1-11-screenshot-1536x864.png 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Gboard-CAPS-1-11-screenshot.png 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p>雖然這頂帽子聽起來非常有趣，但即使你對它非常有興趣也沒有用，因為這頂帽和早前「Gboard BAR」一樣，只是一個玩笑，不會真的公開發售。</p><p>資料來源：<a href="https://tw.news.yahoo.com/googlgboard-caps-032829171.html">Yahoo 新聞</a>、<a href="https://landing.google.co.jp/caps/">Google</a>、<a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=6vib77CUxNM&amp;ab_channel=GoogleJapan">YouTube</a></p><h2> 最新影片</h2><div class="video-container"><iframe loading="lazy" title="最新影片" width="500" height="281" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/videoseries?list=PLiEPZioiGtHw9_9gm4Ty0_pTEviOKNvfl" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" allowfullscreen=""></iframe></div></p>
]]>
            </description>
